mDNS service discovery/zeoconf/bounjour add-on for node.js

=== Build

Currently tested on Mac OS X only. Other platforms will require some tweaking
of wscript.

   node-waf configure build
   sudo node-waf install


=== Examples

   var service = mDNS.createService('eggs_n_bacon', 4321, mDNS.TCP);

   service.announce();
   setTimeout(function() { service.shutdown(); }, 10000);
